@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### List all origin airports
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports
Accept: application/json

###

### Get destinations for a valid origin (LHR)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports/destinations/LHR
Accept: application/json

###

### Get destinations for a valid origin — lowercase (case-insensitive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports/destinations/jfk
Accept: application/json

###

### 404 — Unknown origin code
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports/destinations/XYZ
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 — Invalid code (non-alphabetic character)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports/destinations/1AB
Accept: application/json

###

### 400 — Invalid code (too short)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/airports/destinations/A
Accept: application/json

###
